divs: Sighting Detailsi was walking my Dogs at the usual time 500p.m, and as always, I wasphotographing the sunset.I looked up and at about 1100 oclock, in the s.e. direction, and saw whatappeared to me to be a u.f.o.,.It was easier to see with the naked eye than the 2.8 megapixel digital camerashows.It appeared tp me to be an object, shaped like a teardrop or a seed with alittle bit fatter end then ending in a point on the other end.What amazed me were the flight manovers. It would float foreward,backward, turna circle in the skyI have quite a few pictures that I took with the digital camera. I did set thecamera to the highest resolution, as maybe a phot lab somewhere, can get abetter resolution.What I see on the cameras pics are what I saw in the sky, with the exceptionthat my eye took a better picture.let me know if you would like to see them
